events.name: talk.js
events.description: It's 2016! The first talk.js of this year will be on January 21st. Scheduled Talks • Generative art with Processing.js - Sher Minn Chong • Phasing Out Legacy - Claudio Mettler • NativeScript: Building Native Mobile Apps with JavaScript - Sherman Chen • Building chatapp with Polymer - Zell Liew • Object.observe with ES6 Proxy - Inian Parameshwaran We will have lightning talks of 5~10 minutes and instead use more time for discussions. Location PayPal Singapore Suntec Tower 5 5 Temasek Boulevard #09-01 Singapore Venue, free drinks and pizza sponsored by PayPal. Remember to bring photo ID to get through building security. Feel free to ask questions in the SingaporeJS gitter room:https://gitter.im/SingaporeJS/discussions See you there!
